| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4508 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: eb08b5bc-8f8d-52ee-8940-6a06fa3b0cc4"
